g.", "page": null}, {"id": "s2", "ordinal": 2, "text": "Identify the Tribal contacts and their roles.", "page": null}, {"id": "s3", "ordinal": 3, "text": "Discuss with the Tribal liaison about meeting confidentiality.", "page": null}, {"id": "s4", "ordinal": 4, "text": "Identify issues and topics for discussion.", "page": null}, {"id": "s5", "ordinal": 5, "text": "Determine if the meeting is high level or staff level.", "page": null}, {"id": "s6", "ordinal": 6, "text": "Identify desired outcomes for the meeting.", "page": null}, {"id": "s7", "ordinal": 7, "text": "Document the meeting as publicly available without designation of confidentiality.", "page": null}, {"id": "s8", "ordinal": 8, "text": "Clarify with the Tribal government whether the meeting is public or nonpublic.", "page": null}, {"id": "s9", "ordinal": 9, "text": "Identify meeting participants.", "page": null}, {"id": "s10", "ordinal": 10, "text": "Identify the appropriate rank of the NRC representative.", "page": null}], "preconditions": [{"id": "p1", "text": "Before documenting the meeting, ensure that the Tribal government has not designated it as privileged or confidential."}], "constraints": [], "edges": [{"type": "precedes", "from": "s1", "to": "s2"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s2", "to": "s3"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s3", "to": "s4"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s4", "to": "s5"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s5", "to": "s6"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s6", "to": "s7"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s7", "to": "s8"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s8", "to": "s9"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s9", "to": "s10"}]}, "error": null, "input_tokens": 958, "output_tokens": 578, "cached_tokens": null}, {"chunk_idx": 79, "graph": {"steps": [], "preconditions": [], "constraints": [], "edges": []}, "error": null, "input_tokens": 910, "output_tokens": 23, "cached_tokens": null}, {"chunk_idx": 84, "graph": {"steps": [], "preconditions": [], "constraints": [], "edges": []}, "error": null, "input_tokens": 973, "output_tokens": 23, "cached_tokens": null}, {"chunk_idx": 91, "graph": {"steps": [{"id": "s1", "ordinal": 1, "text": "COMMUNICATE with the Tribe because it is the key to successful relationships.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s2", "ordinal": 2, "text": "FAMILIARIZE YOURSELF with the Tribe’s specific information and understand the history and current issues, concerns, and expertise of the Tribe or Tribes with whom you may work.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s3", "ordinal": 3, "text": "HOLD FACE-TO-FACE MEETINGS to get to know the Tribe and its technical resource staff and council representatives.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s4", "ordinal": 4, "text": "ESTABLISH FAMILIARITY AND CONTINUITY because they are essential elements for establishing and maintaining effective relationships.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s5", "ordinal": 5, "text": "KEEP THE FOCUS WHERE IT BELONGS because Tribes and their concerns should be highlighted during introductions and the meeting table.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s6", "ordinal": 6, "text": "BE ADAPTABLE by exhibiting flexibility, sensitivity, and empathy in Tribal relations.", "page": 29}, {"id": "s7", "ordinal": 7, "text": "BE PATIENT. Take time to understand, communicate with, and work with the Tribes who have an interest in NRC activities.", "page": 29}], "preconditions": [], "constraints": [], "edges": [{"type": "precedes", "from": "s1", "to": "s2"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s2", "to": "s3"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s3", "to": "s4"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s4", "to": "s5"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s5", "to": "s6"}, {"type": "precedes", "from": "s6", "to": "s7"}]}, "error": null, "input_tokens": 865, "output_tokens": 495, "cached_tokens": null}, {"chunk_idx": 98, "graph": {"steps": [], "preconditions": [], "constraints": [], "edges": []}, "error": null, "input_tokens": 679, "output_tokens": 23, "cached_tokens": null}, {"chunk_idx": 103, "graph": {"steps": [], "preconditions": [], "constraints": [], "edges": []}, "error": nu